videos.name: Klaus Schindler - Zeit für Träume // Andrej Istomin
videos.description: The photos in this video were taken by my wife(checkout her channel, by the way:  https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC810...) in Landkreis Dachau(mostly in Schwabhausen and Altomünster). The lovely place where I live.

videos.name: Andrej Istomin - Jenny
videos.description: The melody composed and performed by Andrej Istomin except those telephone sounds.

videos.name: Mauro Giuliani - Sonatina op. 71 no. 1 // Andrej Istomin
videos.description: A little bit of an autumn mood :) Music piece is composed by Mauro Giuliani, called 'Sonatina op71 n°1'. The pictures in slide-show are the reproductions of different Russian painters.

videos.name: Blackmore's Night - Minstrel Hall // Andrej Istomin
videos.description: The piece is composed by Ritchie Blackmore.

videos.name: Fernando Sor - Andante // Andrej Istomin
videos.description: This time I'm playing 'Andante' by Fernando Sor. It is the very first time when I try to create a real video instead of slide show which I did for my previous videos. I hope you like it :)

videos.name: Greensleeves(English traditional) // Andrej Istomin
videos.description: Today I'd like to show you my attempt to play instrumental version of the traditional English song 'Greensleeves'.

videos.name: Ferdinando Carulli - Andantino // Andrej Istomin
videos.description: This summer is really hot here in Germany. I decided to create this small summer video where I'm trying to play nice light piece called 'Andantino' by Ferdinando Carulli (1770-1841).

videos.name: Johann Pachelbel - Sarabande (Guitar + Recorder) // Andrej Istomin
videos.description: I'm finally back after almost a year of silence. During this year I was trying to learn some new skills and bring you a new material which will hopefully entertain you. One of the things which I was focused on at least last half a year was a new instrument: #recorder. I'm far away from being anything good at it, but I already can somehow play a simple melodies.

videos.name: J. S. Bach - Bourrée // Andrej Istomin
videos.description: Thanks for watching this video. If you like it, please subscribe to my channel, comment the videos, 'like' them and share with your friends.
